{{Page version|42.5.1}}
The <code>Icon</code> parameter is used to define the icon of the recipe. This parameter will refer to a texture in the game files. This seems to be used only once in the vanilla recipes with the entry <code>Icon = "Item_WaterDrop",</code> as the icon usually defaults to the items that will be crafted.

==Example==
{{CodeSnip
| lang = lua
| code =
Icon = "Item_WaterDrop",
}}